Usage: setFixedBudget [-help] {[{[{-from {list_of_pins} | -fromFlopsOf {hinst}} {-to {list_of_pins} | -toFlopsOf {hinst}}] | [-through {list_of_hinst}]} {-slack  | -delay } [-add ] <value>] | [-reset ]}

-help                    # Prints out the command usage
<value>                  # delay or slack value (float, required)
-add                     # add the slack/delay to previous value
                         # (bool, optional)
-delay                   # delay value is specified (bool, optional)
-from {list_of_pins}     # from pins to be analaysed (string, required)
-fromFlopsOf {hinst}     # from hierarchical inst for which start pins to be
                         # analaysed (string, required)
-reset                   # reset all previously declared fixed budgets
                         # (bool, optional)
-slack                   # slack value is specified (bool, optional)
-through {list_of_hinst} # through hierarchical insts to be analaysed
                         # (string, required)
-to {list_of_pins}       # to pins to be analaysed (string, required)
-toFlopsOf {hinst}       # to hierarchical inst for which end pins to be
                         # analaysed (string, required)